new_album = im.create_album('New fancy album')
time.sleep(2)
assert not len(new_album.images)
new_album.add_images(IMAGE_IDS)
new_album.refresh()
assert len(new_album.images) == len(IMAGE_IDS)
new_album.delete()
pytest.mark.skipif(refresh_token is None, reason=
    'Cannot run live test without authentication variables.')
